# Redirect based on country
# Redirect Canadian users to .ca domain
/ca/*  https://www.brandgoto.ca/:splat  302  Country=CA
/*     https://www.brandgoto.com/:splat 302  Country=!CA

# Handle direct domain access
https://brandgoto.com/*  https://www.brandgoto.com/:splat  301
https://brandgoto.ca/*   https://www.brandgoto.ca/:splat   301

# Force HTTPS
http://www.brandgoto.com/*  https://www.brandgoto.com/:splat  301
http://www.brandgoto.ca/*   https://www.brandgoto.ca/:splat   301

# Handle root domain redirects
https://brandgoto.com/  https://www.brandgoto.com/  301
https://brandgoto.ca/   https://www.brandgoto.ca/   301

# Handle www to non-www redirects (optional, choose one approach)
# www.brandgoto.com/*  https://brandgoto.com/:splat  301
# www.brandgoto.ca/*   https://brandgoto.ca/:splat   301 